name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
On August 6, a conflict broke out in front of the government of Dingxing County, Baoding City.
The people affected by the flood came to the government to ask for compensation, including some who were dissatisfied with the resettlement, etc.
The special police were dispatched to subdue several people.
Afterwards, the county party secretary went out to communicate with everyone in front of the government, promising that the government would be responsible for medical care, food and accommodation, and even hotel accommodation would be reimbursed.
Online searches for Dingxing County are all videos praising the county party secretary, while the videos of the special police suppressing the victims have all been removed and cannot be searched.
